ZH: 普天之下没有不敬父母的人。
EN: There is no one under the sky who does not respect their parents.
ZH: 普天之下无不散的筵席。
EN: All banquets come to an end eventually under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下没有完美的人。
EN: There is no perfect person under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下只有妈妈好。
EN: Under the sky, only mom is the best.
ZH: 普天之下遍地开花。
EN: Flowers are blooming everywhere under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下都应该追求公平与正义。
EN: Everyone under the sky should pursue fairness and justice.
ZH: 普天之下皆兄弟。
EN: All men are brothers under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下无难事，只怕有心人。
EN: There is no difficult task under the sky, only those who lack determination.
ZH: 普天之下事无绝对。
EN: There is nothing absolute under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下有情人终成眷属。
EN: Under the sky, two people in love will eventually become a couple.
ZH: 普天之下，唯有付出，才会有收获。
EN: Under the sky, only with effort can one reap rewards.
ZH: 普天之下，谁能控制天气？
EN: Under the sky, who can control the weather?
ZH: 普天之下，每个人都有追求幸福的权利。
EN: Under the sky, everyone has the right to pursue happiness.
ZH: 普天之下处处是家。
EN: Every place under the sky feels like home.
ZH: 普天之下人人生而平等。
EN: Everyone is born equal under the sky.
ZH: 普天之下，只有坚持才能获得胜利。
EN: Under the sky, only perseverance leads to victory.
ZH: 普天之下无不是王。
EN: Under the sky, everyone is a king.
ZH: 普天之下，和平是最宝贵的财富。
EN: Under the sky, peace is the most precious treasure.
ZH: 普天之下，事事都有可能。
EN: Under the sky, anything is possible.
ZH: 普天之下没有不泄密的秘密。
EN: Under the sky, there are no secrets that cannot be leaked.
